                <h4>Stream B - Non-CEGEP Students</h4>

    
              <p>12 credits</p>
<p>Non-CEGEP students must take the following courses:</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/cive-208" class="program-course-title">
              CIVE 208 Civil Engineering System Analysis (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-20602" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Civil Engineering (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/609">Faculty of Engineering</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Civil Engineering              : Introduction to civil engineering systems; system modelling process; systems approach and optimization techniques; application of linear programming; simplex method; duality theory; sensitivity analysis; transportation problem; assignment problem; network analysis including critical path method; integer linear programming method.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Naveen Eluru (Fall)                  </p>

    
          <ul class="catalog-notes">
              <li>(3-2-4)</li>
              <li>Prerequisite: COMP 208.</li>
              <li>Corequisite: MATH 264.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

  </div> <!-- /.node -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/cive-311" class="program-course-title">
              CIVE 311 Geotechnical Mechanics (4 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-20616" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
