      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Civil Engineering              : Identification and classification of soils; physical and engineering properties; principle of effective stress; permeability, compressibility, shear strength, stress-strain characteristics; groundwater flow and seepage; earth pressure and retaining structures; stress distributions in soils; settlement; bearing capacity of shallow foundations.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

